room_title: Escape room "Sabotage - Black Ops" by Method of Escape in Fresno
room_description:
You have just received orders: cross enemy lines and infiltrate without detection. Your mission, if you choose to accept it, is to break into the Russian National Defense Control Center and unlock the code to stop the missile strike that would trigger WWIII. You have 60 minutes to save the world from nuclear annihilation! No pressure...
Unique game option allows for 2 groups to race simultaneously in side-by-side rooms.
